ke Suites, Yangon|Lake Suites I]]\n| rowspan=\"3\" | \n| rowspan=\"3\" | [[Yangon]]\n| rowspan=\"3\" | ?\n| rowspan=\"3\" | 32\n| rowspan=\"3\" | ?\n| rowspan=\"3\" | Phase 2 of Myanmar Plaza development <br/> broke ground in 2016\n| rowspan=\"3\" | <ref name=ls-2015>{{cite news | author=Tin Yadana Htun | url=https://www.mmtimes.com/business/property-news/16300-lake-suites-launches-second-tower.html | title=Lake Suites launches second tower | date=2015-09-03 | accessdate=2020-04-11}}</ref><ref name=ls-2016>{{cite news | author=Myat Nyein Aye | url=https://www.mmtimes.com/business/property-news/21071-sales-start-on-third-lake-suites-tower.html | title=Sales start on third Lake Suites tower | date=2016-06-27 | accessdate=2020-04-11}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Lake Suites, Yangon|Lake Suites II]]\n|-\n| [[Lake Suites, Yangon|Lake Suites III]]\n|-\n| [[Emerald Bay, Yangon|Emerald Bay I]]\n| rowspan=\"2\" | \n| rowspan=\"2\" | [[Yangon]]\n| rowspan=\"2\" | ?\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 32\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 2022\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 2x32-story buildings; 3x29-story buildings\n| rowspan=\"2\" | <ref group=note>See {{cite web | url=https://www.cqhp.org/project/emerald-bay-project/ | title=Emerald Bay Project | publisher=CQHP, Republic of the Union of Myanmar | accessdate=2020-04-11}} for the overall project scope. <br/> {{cite news | url=https://elevenmyanmar.com/news/phase-1-of-emerald-bay-high-class-condominium-to-be-completed-in-2022 | title=Phase 1 of Emerald Bay High-Class Condominium to be completed in 2022 | publisher=Eleven Media Group | accessdate=2020-04-11 }} </ref>\n|-\n| [[Emerald Bay, Yangon|Emerald Bay II]]\n|-\n| [[M Tower]]\n| [[File:Hledan center.jpg|alt=|center|frameless|100px]]\n| [[Yangon]]\n| {{convert|111|m|ft|0|abbr=on}}\n| 27\n| 2020\n| \n| <ref group=note>Per the M Tower official web site, {{cite web | url=https://www.mottamadevelopment.com/developments/m-tower/ | title=M Tower | accessdate=2020-04-06}}, the building is 111 meters tall. Compare that to Emporis' estimat