=#000000\n|showValues=offset:1\n|xAxisTitle=Date\n|xAxisAngle=-40\n|type=rect\n|x= 28 Feb, 29 Feb, 1 Mar, 2 Mar, 3 Mar, 4 Mar, 5 Mar, 6 Mar, 7 Mar, 8 Mar, 9 Mar, 10 Mar, 11 Mar, 12 Mar, 13 Mar, 14 Mar, 15 Mar, 16 Mar, 17 Mar, 18 Mar, 19 Mar, 20 Mar, 21 Mar, 22 Mar, 23 Mar, 24 Mar, 25 Mar, 26 Mar,27 Mar, 28 Mar, 29 Mar, 30 Mar, 31 Mar, 1 Apr, 2 Apr, 3 Apr, 4 Apr, 5 Apr, 6 Apr, 7 Apr, 8 Apr, 9 Apr, 10 Apr, 11 Apr, 12 Apr, 13 Apr, 14 Apr, 15 Apr, 16 Apr, 17 Apr, 18 Apr\n|yAxisTitle=No. of new deaths\n|legend=Legend\n|y=0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 0, 1, 2, 1, 2, 2, 1, 10, 14, 21, 16, 43, 31, 33, 56, 48, 54, 87, 156, 181, 260, 209, 180, 381, 563, 569, 684, 708, 621, 441, 786, 938, 881, 980, 917, 737, 717, 778, 761, 861, 847, 888, 596\n|y1Title=Deaths per day\n|yGrid= |xGrid=\n}}\n\n== See also ==\n*[[2020 coronavirus pandemic in England]]\n*[[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Northern Ireland]]\n*[[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Scotland]]\n*[[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Wales]]\n*[[2020 coronavirus pandemic in London]]\n*[[2020 coronavirus pandemic in the Isle of Man]]\n*[[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Jersey]]\n*[[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Guernsey]]\n*[[2020 coronavirus pandemic in British Overseas Territories]]\n\n== Notes ==\n{{reflist|group=\"nb\"}}\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist|colwidth=30em}}\n\n== External links ==\n{{Commons category}}\n* [https://www.nhs.uk/conditions/coronavirus-covid-19/ Coronavirus (COVID-19) on the NHS website]\n* [https://www.gov.uk/coronavirus Coronavirus (COVID-19): UK government information ]\n* [https://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2020/129/contents/made The Health Protection (Coronavirus) Regulations 2020]. Legislation.gov.uk\n* [https://www.publichealth.hscni.net/publications/advice-covid-19-coronavirus Public Health Agency] \u2013 Advice on COVID-19 (coronavirus)\n* [https://www.worldometers.info/coronavirus/country/uk/ Worldometer UK Statistics] \u2013 Worldometer graphs and statistics for the UK\n* [https://coronavirus-global.com/uk Coro